<li><i>The Samurai: A Novel.</i> New York: Columbia University Press, 1992.</li>
<li><i>The Old Man and the Wolves.</i> New York: Columbia University Press, 1994.</li>
<li><i>Possessions: A Novel.</i> New York: Columbia University Press, 1998.</li>
<li><i>Murder in Byzantium.</i> New York: Columbia University Press, 2006.</li>
</ul>
